      • getFullyQualifiedName

        public static java.lang.String getFullyQualifiedName(org.eclipse.jdt.core.IType type)
        Returns the fully qualified name of the given type using '.' as separators. This is a replace for IType.getFullyQualifiedTypeName which uses '$' as separators. As '$' is also a valid character in an id this is ambiguous. JavaCore PR: 1GCFUNT
